public interface MethodInvocationInterceptor extends org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.InvocationInterceptor
An interface redirecting all method interceptions into interceptMethod(org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.InvocationInterceptor.Invocation<T>, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.ReflectiveInvocationContext<java.lang.reflect.Method>, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.ExtensionContext).
